{"arkId":"cl010099005","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010099005","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Montre ronde","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Montre ronde"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Louis XV (1715-1774) (Occident-\u003E\u00e9poque moderne = Ancien R\u00e9gime-\u003Edynastie des Bourbons)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1725 - 1750","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [OArt] Salle 531 - Paul Garnier, Vitrine 1","room":"Salle 531, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1725,"endYear":1750,"imprecision":"","text":"2e quart du XVIIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Koster, William","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"Horloger","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 6224","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"horlogerie ; montre","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Montre ronde, sur le fond une peinture \u00e9maill\u00e9e repr\u00e9sentant M\u00e9l\u00e9agre et Diane d\u0027apr\u00e8s une gravure de Fran\u00e7ois Chauveau (BNF). Sur le pourtour, quatre m\u00e9daillons ovales contenant des paysages de la campagne italienne copi\u00e9s d\u0027apr\u00e8s des gravures de Gabriel P\u00e9relle (BNF), sc\u00e8nes alternent avec des fleurons en cama\u00efeu rouge. Contre-\u00e9mail figurant l\u0027Enl\u00e8vement d\u0027Amphitrite par Neptune d\u0027apr\u00e8s une oeuvre de Simon Vouet grav\u00e9e par Michel Dorigny (BNF). Cadran \u00e0 chiffres romains et arabes, deux aiguilles serties de roses de diamant. Mouvement dot\u00e9 d\u0027un \u00e9chappement \u00e0 roue de rencontre, une fus\u00e9e avec cha\u00eene. Balancier \u00e0 ressort-spiral-r\u00e9glant prot\u00e9g\u00e9 par un coq ajour\u00e9 et grav\u00e9 de rinceaux \u00e0 feuilles d\u0027acanthe asym\u00e9triques.","inscriptions":"Signature : \r ; mouvement sign\u00e9 : Wm Koster Amsterdam","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"5,4","displayDimension":"5,4 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"4,3","displayDimension":"4,3 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Epaisseur","value":"2,5","displayDimension":"2,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : diamant\r\nMat\u00e9riau : laiton\r\nTechnique : techniques m\u00e9tal (orf\u00e8vrerie)\r\nTechnique : \u00e9maill\u00e9 = \u00e9maillage = \u00e9mail = \u00e9maux (techniques m\u00e9tal)","placeOfCreation":"Amsterdam (Europe-\u003EPays-Bas = Pays Bas = Hollande)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Collection Jean-Charles Seguin (1857-1908), Paris. Legs, J.-Ch. Seguin, 1908.","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"M. Seguin, Jean-Charles","note":"","role":", Donateur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"legs","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date","value":"1908","startYear":1908,"endYear":1908}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"legs"}],"period":[{"value":"Louis XV (1715-1774)"}],"place":[{"value":"Amsterdam"}],"objectType":[{"value":"horlogerie"},{"value":"montre"}]},"bibliography":[{"bibliographyRef":"Cardinal, Catherine, Les montres et horloges de table du mus\u00e9e du Louvre, Tome 2, Paris, RMN, 2000","bibliographyDate":"